Agent orientation lives in [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md) — read it first. Normative project rules will live in `docs/` as the handbook grows.

Topic-specific guidance is loaded on demand via [.cursor/rules/](mdc:.cursor/rules/) and the canonical bodies in [.agents/skills/](mdc:.agents/skills/) (shared with Claude Code, Codex CLI, and Gemini CLI).

Commands: `pnpm install`, `pnpm run dev`, `pnpm run build`, `pnpm run build:pages`, `pnpm run generate`, `pnpm run preview`. Run `pnpm run build:pages` before declaring a deploy-related task complete.
